<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>420</hymn_number>
<author>N. Rabenimanana</author>
<title>Ry Raiko feno antra FFPM420</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Ry Raiko feno antra,
 Inty aho fa ory ;
 Mijaly sy mahantra,
 Ka tsy mahatraka akory,
 Jesosy no nilonjy
 Ny ota vitanao ;
 Ny rany mahavonjy,
 Nomeny ho anao.

[V2]
 Nandao ny tavanao,
 Nikaro-java-tsoa ;
 Korana sy lalao,
 Sambo-drivotra avokoa.
 Jesosy ..sns.

[V3]
 Izaho fahavalo
 Fa tsy narianao,
 Ny loza natakalo
 Hasambaram-baovao.
 Jesosy ..sns.

[V4]
 Hanompo no iriko
 Fa zanaka nania,
 Ry hany itokiako
 Mba ho Tompoko doria.
 Jesosy ..sns.</lyrics>
</song>